description:
Prompt PDF here: https://markmanson.net/aiprompts

In this video, I put AI to the test. Not as a productivity hack, but as a personal growth tool. Everyone’s used ChatGPT to plan vacations or write emails, but few know how to actually train it to make you sharper, more self-aware, and more effective. I built 7 powerful AI prompts designed to help you uncover blind spots, build better habits, and extract real insight from your own behavior. You’ll see exactly how to structure prompts for maximum depth, how different models think, and how to turn AI into the ultimate self-improvement coach. Plus, I’m giving all 7 prompts away free to use, no fluff.
